    * Kahoot was good
        * But student engagement decreased over time. Once students started trailing behind in the leaderboard they cared less. 
    * WWTBAM was good
        * Did not suffer like kahoot in terms of engagement. 
    * Codeacademy
        * Some error messages were too vague
